    "description": "It is said that there is a treasure hidden in this land...<br>Can you find it? Find it! Everything in the world will be there. CRASH-SAN destroys the spirit. Use jumps and guns to get the treasure before the spirit is destroyed. Will your spirit remain normal?<br>One adventurer travels across a vast land in search of a vast amount of treasure.<br>Become an adventurer and overcome various challenges to become a brave champion who conquers the world.<br>Collect gold coins scattered around the world. When all the pieces are in place, the doors of the world will open.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mouse and keyboard support.<br></li><li>Action game.<br></li><li>Exhilarating and wonderful music.<br></li><li>Aim for the goal with limited lives.<br></li><li>There is a save point, so save often!<br></li><li>Three different stages await you.<br></li><li>Each stage has traps to make you suffer.<br></li><li>The enemy is coming at you, avoid him!<br></li><li>Play alone.<br></li><li>Multi-compatible...<br></li><li>You will feel a sense of accomplishment when you clear a stage after challenging it many times.</li></ul>",
